Here's a JavaScript function that computes the n-th Fibonacci number mod p:

```javascript
function fibonacciModulo(n, p) {
  if (n <= 1) {
    return n;
  }

  let a = 0;
  let b = 1;

  for (let I = 2; I <= n; i++) {
    let c = (a + b) % p;
    a = b;
    b = c;
  }

  return b;
}
```

